name.ja: <ruby>Ｎｏ．<rt>ナンバーズ</rt></ruby>６９ <ruby>紋章神<rt>ゴッド・メダリオン</rt></ruby>コート・オブ・アームズ－ゴッド・レイジ
name.ja_romaji: Nanbāzu Rokujūkyū Goddo Medarion Kōto Obu Āmuzu - Goddo Reiji

text.en:
5 Level 4 monsters
Cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; its name becomes "Unknown". When a monster effect activated by your opponent resolves, if that monster's name is "Unknown", negate that activated effect.
